cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM 

This paper deals with visual-semantic embedding, which involves the intersection of computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). However, the paper also proposes a new loss function and metric for ranking, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL) techniques. Finally, the paper uses datasets that involve multimedia (cs.MM) such as images and text.
